- Stops on first success
- Proper timeout per attempt
- Clear logging of attempts and results
- Returns success with proxy ID that worked","status":"in_progress","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","assignee":"","owner":"jeff141421@gmail.com","created_at":"2026-01-18T19:05:25.704408915Z","created_by":"Dicklesworthstone","updated_at":"2026-01-22T04:03:34.901235756Z","compaction_level":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"rust_proxy-7nv","depends_on_id":"rust_proxy-ny9","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-01-18T19:07:30.980704217Z","created_by":"Dicklesworthstone","metadata":"","thread_id":""}]}
